@c -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
@node Graphics
@section Graphics

@code{(pnm graphics)} module contains simple pixel manipulation methods.

@deffn  {Method} pnm-image-pixel (image <pbm-ascii-image>) (index <number>)
@deffnx {Method} pnm-image-pixel (image <pbm-binary-image>) (index <number>)
Get a pixel specified by an @var{index} from an @var{image}.  Return the pixel
as a number or throw a pnm-error on error.
@end deffn

@deffn  {Method} pnm-image-pixel (image <pbm-ascii-image>) @
                                 (x <number>) @
                                 (y <number>)
@deffnx {Method} pnm-image-pixel (image <pbm-binary-image>) @
                                 (x <number>) @
                                 (y <number>)
Get a pixel specified by @var{x} and @var{y} Cartesian coordinates from an
@var{image}.  Return the pixel as a number or throw a pnm-error on error.
@end deffn

@deffn  {Method} pnm-image-pixel-set! (image <pbm-ascii-image>) @
                                      (index <number>) @
                                      (value <number>)
@deffnx {Method} pnm-image-pixel-set! (image <pbm-binary-image>) @
                                      (index <number>) @
                                      (value <number>)
Set a pixel specified by @var{index} offset in an @var{image} to the specified
@var{value}.  Return value is undefined.
@end deffn

@deffn  {Method} pnm-image-pixel-set! (image <pbm-ascii-image>) @
                                      (x <number>) @
                                      (y <number>) @
                                      (value <number>)
@deffnx {Method} pnm-image-pixel-set! (image <pbm-binary-image>) @
                                      (x <number>) @
                                      (y <number>) @
                                      (value <number>)
Set a pixel specified by @var{x} and @var{y} Cartesian coordinates offset in
an @var{image} to the specified @var{value}.  Return value is undefined.
@end deffn

